WASHINGTON, May 15 (Xinhua) -- U.S. Attorney General Janet Reno has authorized prosecutors to seek the death penalty for Unabomber suspect Theodore Kaczynski, Justice Department official and a lawyer for the Kaczynski family said Thursday.
WASHINGTON, January 5 (Xinhua) -- The trial of former math professor Theodore Kaczynski, accused of serial killings with mail-bombs over an 18-year period, is set to open Monday in Sacramento, California, where police say the suspect killed two people.
